  "combined_text": "--- Main Page ---\nRoswell - Standard Restaurant Group\nWELCOME TO The Standard at Roswell\nIN HISTORIC DOWNTOWN ROSWEL at the intersection of Norcross and Alpharetta\nClick Here to Order Takeout\nThe Standard Menu\nGet in Touch\nAbout The Standard at Roswell\nPizza, calzones, wings, an ever changing assortment of craft and imported beers, live music, and the friendliest bar in town. The Standard at Roswell is a great place to enjoy all of this – and the crowds that gather here will tell you the same. So come on by the Standard and see for yourself. And if your friends aren’t already there, you will soon make new ones. We offer indoor and outdoor dining with a casual atmosphere. Enjoy lunch, dinner or a little nightlife at one of Downtown Roswell’s most popular spots.\nView Our Menu\nTour the standard at roswell\nThe Dishes\nThe Supreme\nStandard Menu\nStandard Wings\nStandard Burger\nChicken Finger Plate\nThe Classic\nStrawberry Spring Salad\nItalian Sammie\nGarlic “Nots”\nHummus\nHummus & Garlic “Nots”\nThe Astro Pizza\nContact Our Roswell Location\nNAME\nPHONE\nEMAIL ADDRESS\nCHOOSE YOUR LOCATION\nCHOOSE YOUR LOCATION\nAlpharetta\nRoswell\nYOUR MESSAGES\nContact Us\n* For large reservations, please call the desired location during business hours\n\n--- Page: /wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1-STNDRD_MenuDesign_BILLS_2021Season-1.pdf ---\n%PDF-1.5\r%����\n16 0 obj\r<\n>\rendobj\r             \r64 0 obj\r<\n>/Filter/FlateDecode/ID[\n]/Index[16 96]/Info 15 0 R/Length 145/Prev 3056801/Root 17 0 R/Size 112/Type/XRef/W[1 3 1]>>stream\nh�bbd`\u0010``b``^\u0002\"\u0019��H�H\u0010ɕ\u0001\"����~\u0010ɺ\t��\r&�A${6�-\nf_\u0007��b ��\bDr���\u0004˚��K��\u000f�H��@�q\u0005\u000f���\u0002H\ni�\u0000I\u0016�i`��\\��\b��Ȁ��@�!�6a�`�+\u001d�\fL�P�\u000f�\u0005\f�Q\u0012J�g`j�\f\u0010`\u0000H?\u0019X\rendstream\rendobj\rstartxref\r0\r%%EOF\r                                                                                                                         \r111 0